<div><font face="Arial" size="4" style="font-size: 14pt; "><b>General data quality</b></font></div>
<div><font face="Arial"><br />
    </font></div>
<div><font face="Arial" size="4">Occasionally a user may notice data that looks to be incorrect (such as address details and phone numbers). First check that this is not simply a difference between the old Level 5 Customer and the new Customer as these are not necessarily classified in the same way.  If the data is then found to be incorrect, report this to your Super User.</font></div>
